[options="header",cols="10%,20%,10%,60%"]
|======

| Name
| Type
| Mandatory
| Description


| order
| string
| false
| Field order (ASC/DESC/UNSORTED) to sort the result by. Default: UNSORTED. 

| page
| number
| false
| Number of page to be loaded. Default: 1. 

| perPage
| number
| false
| Number of elements per page.

| sortBy
| string
| false
| Field name to sort the result by.

